Package levels

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LevelLoader
    A.
    LevelSaver
    The interface for the savers, has method that gets a filename, a level, and a general output stream to write the level to.
    Movable
    Interface for items that can move.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Box
    Item of type box.
    Character
    Item of type Character.
    Clock
    Clock that counts time to finish level.
    Item
    Item in the game.
    Level
    Level class, has a board that is array list of array lists, array list of chars and array list of boxes.
    LoaderFactory
    The Factory that creates loaders - by extensions.
    MovableItem
    Superclass for movable items (now: box,char).
    MyObjectLevelLoader
    Object loader - by serialization.
    MyObjectLevelSaver
    Object saver - by serialization.
    MyTextLevelLoader
    Text loader - creates a level, and fills arraylists with items.
    MyTextLevelSaver
    Text saver - convert the level to a sign board (char matrix) and saves it.
    MyXMLLevelLoader
    XML loader - by serialization.
    MyXMLLevelSaver
    XML saver - by serialization.
    Position
    Holds x,y coordinates.
    SaverFactory
    The Factory that creates savers - by extensions.
    Serialization
    Reads and writes to objects by serialization.
    Star
    A target for boxes.
    Wall
    A wall item.
